{"tid":2180531,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解所有大廈點都會擺個阿叔實Q喺門口？","createTime":"2020-08-30T02:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:57:45.000Z","uid":322642,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ccb07c9076fff27fce74b434a3a9f0a1df74a31","tid":2180531,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"冇人知個實Q好無抽, 反應快唔快<br />\n但擺咗條友向外望就點都有一定阻嚇作用<br />\n<br />\n所有活動無論係追思好定連儂好<br />\n都唔好所有人背住後面公眾環境去做嘢<br />\n<br />\n請至少擺一至兩個人係向外視察環境,<br />\n可能你身上咩都冇(或者你有)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你最少都一定有部電話 <br />\n可以stand by向外拍低所有情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指意圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PK8hY0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPK8hY0B.jpg&h=d04bce0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><br />\n盡量最大力度保護自己<br />\n不流血 不受傷 不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"980d650a57c47aa30955646f17f746d7fbf58273","tid":2180531,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"仲要有隱敝cam拍住"},{"pid":"7eabb0d62ec7deb41541b309cd57106fcd028351","tid":2180531,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980d650a57c47aa30955646f17f746d7fbf58273","tid":2180531,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"仲要有隱敝cam拍住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前終國酒店條片大家知道啲鏡頭可以好細<br />\n人哋用嚟做壞事 我哋可以用嚟保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66843490b3ad307aa171f2859e0092b101eb645a","tid":2180531,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020